635
00:35:35.522 --> 00:35:38.691
When I was little. I used to cry
every time we drove over a bridge.

636
00:35:38.692 --> 00:35:39.858
I don't know why.

637
00:35:39.859 --> 00:35:41.902
My mom used to try to distract me...

638
