696
00:38:30.572 --> 00:38:33.031
Well. you should be.

697
00:38:33.032 --> 00:38:35.284
But I mean. seriously.
it was just a list.

698
00:38:35.285 --> 00:38:37.035
Like. a stupid high school thing.

699
00:38:37.036 --> 00:38:40.381
That fucking list. I wish I
never touched that fucking list.

700
00:38:41.332 --> 00:38:42.479
Why did you?

701
00:38:42.504 --> 00:38:44.168
I don't know. Bryce started it.

702
00:38:44.169 --> 00:38:46.336
All the guys were
working on it at lunch.

703
