friends with those guys?

704
00:38:48.506 --> 00:38:50.215
Justin. Zach. Bryce.

705
00:38:50.216 --> 00:38:52.602
No. see. I'm not friends with Bryce.

706
00:38:53.386 --> 00:38:54.553
But the other guys.

707
00:38:54.554 --> 00:38:57.306
Zach and I got to be friends last year.

708
00:38:57.307 --> 00:38:59.308
and he's always hanging around Justin.

709
