Also. didn't totally suck at school
that Justin Foley liked me back then.

712
00:39:09.694 --> 00:39:11.245
Okay. back then.

713
00:39:11.946 --> 00:39:13.447
Why are you friends now?

714
00:39:13.448 --> 00:39:17.242
Because if I stop hanging out.
they're gonna know something's up.

715
00:39:17.243 --> 00:39:19.077
I shouldn't even be talking to you.

716
00:39:19.078 --> 00:39:20.954
- Seriously?
- Yes.

717
00:39:20.955 --> 00:39:23.749
But you don't even
