725
00:39:50.068 --> 00:39:52.578
You know? I-I loved her.

726
00:39:52.987 --> 00:39:55.790
And it did piss Jessica
off. but not at me.

727
00:39:56.074 --> 00:39:57.241
<i>At Hannah.</i>

728
00:39:57.242 --> 00:39:58.685
Alex did this on his own.

729
00:39:58.710 --> 00:40:01.304
He just broke up with me on his own.

730
00:40:01.329 --> 00:40:02.558
